<lb n="0922b02"/><head type="no">No. 1407</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0922b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0922012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說辟除諸惡陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0922b04"/>
<lb n="0922b05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0922013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（西天…臣））十九字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0922013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿明教大師臣）十九字＝（三藏法師）四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0922013"><lem>西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0922b06"/>明教大師臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿明教大師臣</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0922b07"/><p>爾時世尊告阿難言。我見世間災濔起時。遂
<lb n="0922b08"/>生飛蝗及與毒蟲。乃至蚊虻虎狼處處增盛。
<lb n="0922b09"/>致傷苗稼或傷菜果。遂令國內漸成飢饉。惱
<lb n="0922b10"/>害眾生不得安隱。我今為汝宣說辟除諸惡
<lb n="0922b11"/>陀羅尼。若有眾生<note n="0922014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝至【元】【明】</note><app n="0922014"><lem>志</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>心持誦。非獨自利亦利
<lb n="0922b12"/>他人。若持誦人欲作成就法者。先須潔淨齋
<lb n="0922b13"/>戒發誠諦心。誦陀羅尼滿十萬遍已成精熟。
<lb n="0922b14"/>然可隨處作成就法。若作法者復潔淨已。然
<lb n="0922b15"/>誦諸佛菩薩名號請求加被。乃將少沙盛淨
<lb n="0922b16"/>器<note n="0922015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中字以下麗本缺，依明本補載之</note>中。誦陀羅尼八百遍加持前沙。於有毒蟲
<lb n="0922b17"/>處散擲。一切毒蟲皆悉辟除即說陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0922b18"/><p type="dharani">曩莫薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱&CB00155;地薩埵曩<note place="inline">引一</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>釤
<lb n="0922b19"/><note place="inline">引</note>曩莫塞訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>埵<note place="inline">引二</note>壹&CB00805;<note place="inline">引</note>尾&CB00853;<note place="inline">切身</note>&CB00425;
<lb n="0922b20"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>踰<note place="inline">引</note>惹夜<note place="inline">引</note>彌<note place="inline">三</note>壹&CB00792;尾&CB00853;三蜜哩<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0922b21"/>迭&CB00418;彌<note place="inline">引四</note>怛&CB00853;<note place="inline">切身</note>他<note place="inline">引五</note>訶訶訶<note place="inline">六</note>黎黎黎
<lb n="0922b22"/><note place="inline">七</note>酇酇酇<note place="inline">八</note>酇沙野<note place="inline">九</note>呬呬<note place="inline">十</note>詰詰<note place="inline">十一</note>蜜哩蜜
<lb n="0922b23"/>哩<note place="inline">十二</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>拏迦<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引十三</note>敦拏滿唐羯嚕
<lb n="0922b24"/>彌娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十四</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>摩舍迦<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0922b25"/>喃<note place="inline">引十五</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>莽酤拏<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引十六</note>薩哩
<lb n="0922b26"/>微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;輸迦<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引十七</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>遏
<lb n="0922b27"/>說<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引十八</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>謨<note place="inline">引</note>沙迦<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引十九</note>
<lb n="0922b28"/>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>戍迦舍<note place="inline">引</note>哩迦喃<note place="inline">引二十</note>薩哩微
<lb n="0922b29"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>蘇<note place="inline">引</note>羯囉<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引二十一</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>末
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1407.0922c" n="0922c"/>
<lb n="0922c01"/>哩羯<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引二十二</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤<note place="inline">引</note>末羅曩<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0922c02"/>喃<note place="inline">引二十三</note>薩哩微<note place="inline">二合引</note>釤薩寫伽<note place="inline">引</note>怛迦<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note place="inline">引二十四</note>
<lb n="0922c03"/>敦拏滿馱羯嚕彌娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引二十五</note></p>
<lb n="0922c04"/><p>爾時阿難。得聞世尊說是辟除諸惡陀羅尼
<lb n="0922c05"/>已。歡喜信受禮佛而退</p>
<lb n="0922c06"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說辟除諸惡陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
